    "body": "\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Added floating-point RNG output (single/double precision) and a selectable RNG generator option for initialization.\n* **Performance**\n  * Improved vectorization behavior so RNG calls can be vectorized more effectively across lanes.\n* **Tests**\n  * Expanded tests to exercise multiple RNG generators and multiple RNG-generated outputs per run.\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can customize this high-level summary in your review settings.</sub>\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
